	plugins/gtalk-plugin.c, plugins/jabber-plugin.c,
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/Makefile.am,
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-item.[hc],
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-plugin.[hc],
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-service.[hc],
	plugins/sip-plugin.c, src/accounts-wizard-dialog.c:
	Introduce the AccountService class, whose objects represent the
	Telepathy profiles, to allow for a plugin to provide support for more
	than one profile.

2007-08-02  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* libaccounts/account-edit-context.h, libaccounts/account-item.[hc],
	libaccounts/account-plugin-manager.[hc],
	libaccounts/account-plugin.[hc], libaccounts/accounts-list.h,
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-item.[hc],
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-plugin.c,
	src/accounts-wizard-dialog.c:
	Allow the AccountItem to hold a reference to the AccountPlugin, since
	that was done in the Rtcom implementations anyway.

=== osso-accounts 3.27 ===
	
2007-07-26  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* plugins/sip-advanced.glade:
	* plugins/sip-plugin.c: (on_advanced_clicked):
	Enable "Auto-detect STUN" by default as it used to be

=== osso-accounts 3.26 ===
	
