	* plugins/sip-advanced.glade:
	* plugins/sip-plugin.c: (auto_stun_toggled_cb),
	(on_advanced_clicked):
	Bind "Auto-detect STUN" to "discover-stun" parameter.
	For the time being, bind "Authentication user name" to
	"auth-user" instead of less useful "extra-auth-user" param.
	
