=== osso-accounts 3.15 ===
	
2007-06-27  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-username.c:
	Rewrite check for account uniqueness: don't assume that the account
	returned by mc_account_lookup_with_profile() will have the same
	account name, since it is also checking for the normalized name.
	Instead, a straight comparison of the McAccount pointers is safer.
	Fixes: NB#61858.

=== osso-accounts 3.14 ===
	
