	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-item.c:
	Make sure we are not using a NULL string with strcmp.

=== osso-accounts 3.13 ===
	
2007-06-20  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-item.c:
	Make sure we don't store an uninitialized account name.

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-plugin.c:
	Unref the account item, since the context takes ownership of it.

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-context.c:
	Use g_object_ref_sink() instead of g_object_ref(), since pages might
	have a floating reference.
	
	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-widget.c:
	Unref the account item on dispose.

2007-06-19  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-displayname.c:
	Avoid warnings from setting NULL values in the entry
	
	* src/accounts-wizard-dialog.c:
	Unref objects in destroy rather than finalize.
	Increase debug - there's a plenty of reference leaks to be plugged

2007-06-19  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* libaccounts/account-plugin.c:
	Disconnect the signal handler on the AccountsList before being
	disposed.

=== osso-accounts 3.12 ===

