	* configure.ac:
	* src/Makefile.am:
	Depend on hildon-help instead of osso-help
	
	* libaccounts/account-plugin-manager.c:
	(account_plugin_manager_dispose),
	(account_plugin_manager_finalize),
	(account_plugin_manager_class_init):
	Handle dispose properly
	
	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-plugin.c:
	(rtcom_account_plugin_get_account_by_name), (on_account_changed),
	(on_account_deleted), (on_account_disabled), (on_account_enabled):
	Revert the change from 2007-06-06 as useless
	
	* src/accounts-ui.c: (new_clicked_cb), (accounts_ui_init),
	(accounts_ui_set_property), (accounts_ui_destroy),
	(accounts_ui_finalize), (accounts_ui_class_init),
	(accounts_ui_run_in_wizard_mode):
	Use hildon-help API instead of osso-help. Unref objects in destroy
	rather than finalize, so that circular refs do not result in leaks.

