=== osso-accounts 3.0 ===

2007-06-07  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* configure.ac: Version 3.0.

2007-06-06  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* configure.ac:
	* src/osso-accounts-settings.pc.in:
	Add a configuration file for other applications' convenience

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-plugin.c:
	(rtcom_account_plugin_get_account_by_name), (on_account_changed),
	(on_account_deleted):
	Reference the AccountItem just in case (might fix ugly warnings that
	occurred as a side-effect of all plugins handling all monitor events)

2007-06-06  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* plugins/gtalk-existing-account.glade,
	plugins/jabber-existing-account.glade,
	plugins/jabber-new-account.glade,
	plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-username.[hc],
	plugins/sip-existing-account.glade:
	Correct the check for invalid characters in the username.

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-account-plugin.c:
	Only monitor account items belonging to this plugin.

	* configure.ac, plugins/Makefile.am, plugins/google-talk.profile,
	plugins/jabber.profile, plugins/sip.profile:
	Add profile files.

	* plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/rtcom-username.c:
	Fix check for uniqueness. Fix a compilation warning.

	* plugins/gtalk-plugin.c:
	In the advanced settings hash table, store the widget itself instead
	of its name.

2007-06-05  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* src/accounts-wizard-dialog.c: (page_async_cb),
	(button_clicked_cb):
	Disable the "Previous" button while waiting for an async page to
	complete.

	* autogen.sh:
	Do not run make automatically.

	* configure.ac:
	* plugins/Makefile.am:
	* src/Makefile.am:
	* src/main.c:
	* src/osso-accounts.desktop:
	Pluginize the UI.

2007-06-05  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* plugins/jabber-plugin.c:
	Use an animation while the account is being registered.
	Free the RegisterData struct as soon as registration procedure is
	completed.
	Don't crash if next button is pressed when a registration is already
	going on.
	Dim the "back" and "next" buttons while registering.

	* plugins/jabber-plugin.c:
	Set the toplevel window as parent for the banner messages.

	* plugins/jabber-plugin.c:
	Check and ask for connectivity.

2007-06-05  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* src/accounts-wizard-dialog.c: (show_error_as_banner),
	(page_async_cb), (button_clicked_cb), (next_insensitive_cb):
	Handle the "page-async" signal. Avoid requesting pages
	while waiting for the page to become ready.

2007-06-05  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* plugins/sip-advanced.glade:
	* plugins/sip-plugin.c: (on_store_settings),
	(transport_combo_changed_cb), (auto_stun_toggled_cb),
	(on_advanced_clicked):
	Update port when changing between TLS and non-TLS transports.
	Make auto-detect STUN setting work.
	
