	* src/accounts-ui.c: (enable_toggled_cb), (construct_tree_view),
	(sort_func), (add_item_to_store), (item_added_cb),
	(item_removed_cb), (accounts_ui_init), (accounts_ui_finalize),
	(accounts_ui_class_init): Set up GtkListStore with all the needed columns, plus
	make it and the GtkTreeView sortable.

	* src/main.c: (execute): Set dialog title

2007-04-24  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* libaccounts/accounts-list.c:
	Add "add" and "remove" signals to the AccountsList interface.

	* libaccounts/account-plugin-manager.[hc]:
	Add AccountsList parameter to account_plugin_manager_new(), and let
	the manager initialize the plugins.

	* configure.ac, plugins/Makefile.am, plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts/*:
	Add plugins/libosso-rtcom-accounts for common Rtcom account
	functionality.

2007-04-23  Lassi Syrjala  <lassi.syrjala@nokia.com>

	* Makefile.am:
	Build libaccounts/ before src/

	* configure.ac:
	* src/Makefile.am:
	Enable l10n support; add checks for hildon-control-panel and libosso

	* src/accounts-ui.h:
	Derive from GtkDialog instead of GObject

	* src/accounts-ui.c:
	Add buttons to action area

	* src/accounts-wizard-dialog.[hc]:
	Clean up

	* src/main.c: (execute), (save_state), (main):
	Add execute and save_state functions as required by the CP iface

	* src/accounts-ui.c: (construct_tree_view), (accounts_ui_init):
	Construct a tree view for displaying the accounts

2007-04-23  Alberto Mardegan  <alberto.mardegan@nokia.com>

	* libaccounts/account-item.[hc]:
	Implement properties, add account_item_set_enabled() method.

	* libaccounts/Makefile.am:
	* libaccounts/account-error.h:
	Add account-error.h, for error definitions.

	* libaccounts/account-plugin-manager.c:
	Implement account_plugin_manager_get_plugin().

	* libaccounts/account-plugin.[hc]:
	Make account_plugin_get_name() return a const string.

	* libaccounts/account-plugin-loader.[hc], libaccounts/Makefile.am:
	Added AccountPluginLoader class, for implementing plugins as
	GTypeModule.

	* libaccounts/account-plugin.[hc]:
	Add the AccountsList object as a parameter for setup(), and also as a
	read-only property.

	* libaccounts/account-plugin-manager.c:
	Implement account_plugin_manager_list().

